<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Blog</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/header.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/blog.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header', { title: 'Blog' }) %>

    <section class="blog-section">
        <h2>Share Your Blog</h2>
        <form class="blog-form">
            <input type="text" placeholder="Your Name" required class="form-input">
            <input type="text" placeholder="Blog Title" required class="form-input">
            <textarea placeholder="Write your blog here..." required class="form-textarea"></textarea>
            <button type="submit" class="submit-button">Submit Blog</button>
        </form>

        <h3>Recent Blogs</h3>
        <div class="blog-list">
            <article class="blog-post">
                <h4>The Beauty of Indian Festivals</h4>
                <p><strong>By:</strong> Akash Sundar</p>
                <p>India's festivals are vibrant and full of life. Each festival brings unique traditions and unites people in celebration.</p>
            </article>

            <article class="blog-post">
                <h4>Exploring the Cuisine of South India</h4>
                <p><strong>By:</strong> Ansaf Shan</p>
                <p>South Indian food is a delightful journey with flavors ranging from tangy sambar to crispy dosas. A must-try for food lovers!</p>
            </article>

            <article class="blog-post">
                <h4>My First Trip to Rajasthan</h4>
                <p><strong>By:</strong> Anfaal Kasim</p>
                <p>Visiting Rajasthan was a dream come true! The palaces, forts, and colorful culture left me in awe. Highly recommend a visit.</p>
            </article>

            <article class="blog-post">
                <h4>Indian Handicrafts: A Timeless Tradition</h4>
                <p><strong>By:</strong> Athul Krishna A</p>
                <p>The art of Indian handicrafts showcases the country's rich heritage. From pottery to embroidery, each piece tells a story.</p>
            </article>
        </div>
    </section>

</body>
<%- include('partials/footer') %>
</html>
